<p><a name="History" id="History"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Raytheon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:202px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Raytheon1934TubeBox.PNG" class="image" title="An early Raytheon Tube Box"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ef/Raytheon1934TubeBox.PNG/200px-Raytheon1934TubeBox.PNG" width="200" height="565" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
